{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/people/jacqui-smith","content_id":"8d7c6906-f1dd-4a7d-ba70-ecd1a08aefe6","description":"The Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern was appointed Minister of State (Minister for Skills) in the Department for Education on 6 July 2024. This role also became part of the Department for Work and Pensions on 6 September 2025. Since 4 March 2025, the Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern has also served as Minister of State (Minister for Women and Equalities). She previously served as a Government Spokesperson for Equalities between 8 October 2024 and 4 March 2025.","details":{"body":"<p>The Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern was appointed Minister of State (Minister for Skills) in the Department for Education on 6 July 2024. This role also became part of the Department for Work and Pensions on 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>Since 4 March 2025, the Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern has also served as Minister of State (Minister for Women and Equalities).</p>\n\n<p>She previously served  as a Government Spokesperson for Equalities between 8 October 2024 and 4 March 2025.</p>\n","full_name":"Baroness Smith of Malvern","image":{"alt_text":"The Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/669551bfa3c2a28abb50cfe8/s465_Jacqui_Smith_960x640.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":true},"document_type":"person","first_published_at":"2024-07-06T20:57:45+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/jacqui-smith","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/jacqui-smith","base_path":"/government/people/jacqui-smith","content_id":"8d7c6906-f1dd-4a7d-ba70-ecd1a08aefe6","document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-12-05T16:50:06Z","schema_name":"person","title":"The Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/jacqui-smith","withdrawn":false}],"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"33e1de69-b71e-4022-945